4.5. Mediation analysis: Profitability and financing constraints
To delve deeper into the mechanisms through which AI adoption
influences corporate financialization, we examine two potential mediating
pathways: enhanced profitability and reduced financing constraints.
Understanding these channels is crucial for both theoretical
development and practical implications, as it reveals not merely
whether AI affects financialization, but how and why this relationship
operates. We employ the Baron and Kenny mediation framework, conducting
formal mediation tests through sequential regression models
that isolate the indirect effects operating through each proposed
mediator.
